---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy — SwarmHaul" description="Privacy policy for SwarmHaul.">
  <main class="max-w-[720px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-24">
    <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[11px] tracking-[0.14em] text-[var(--color-ash)] hover:text-[var(--color-phosphor)] mb-12">
      ← BACK
    </a>

    <h1 class="text-[28px] font-bold tracking-tight mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-[12px] text-[var(--color-ash)] tracking-[0.1em] mb-12">Datenschutzerklärung — Last updated April 2026</p>

    <section class="space-y-8 text-[13px] text-[var(--color-steel)] leading-relaxed">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-[11px] tracking-[0.14em] text-[var(--color-ash)] mb-3">CONTROLLER</h2>
        <p>
          Sharang Parnerkar<br />
          Matthias-Claudius-Strasse 24, 78234 Engen, Germany<br />
          <a href="mailto:parnerkarsharang@gmail.com" class="text-[var(--color-phosphor)] hover:underline">parnerkarsharang@gmail.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-[11px] tracking-[0.14em] text-[var(--color-ash)] mb-3">DATA WE COLLECT</h2>
        <p>This site does not actively collect personal data. GitHub Pages (our hosting provider) may log standard server access data — IP address (anonymised), browser type, and timestamp — for technical operation purposes. We have no access to or control over these logs.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-[11px] tracking-[0.14em] text-[var(--color-ash)] mb-3">FEEDBACK WIDGET (SEGGWAT)</h2>
        <p>This site uses <a href="https://seggwat.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="text-[var(--color-phosphor)] hover:underline">Seggwat</a> for user feedback. If you submit feedback, Seggwat processes the content of your message and any screenshot you choose to attach. Seggwat's own privacy policy governs that data. No feedback is submitted unless you actively click the widget and send a message.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-[11px] tracking-[0.14em] text-[var(--color-ash)] mb-3">HOSTING</h2>
        <p>This site is hosted on GitHub Pages. GitHub's <a href="https://docs.github.com/en/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-general-privacy-statement" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="text-[var(--color-phosphor)] hover:underline">Privacy Statement ↗</a> applies.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-[11px] tracking-[0.14em] text-[var(--color-ash)] mb-3">EXTERNAL LINKS</h2>
        <p>Links to GitHub, Colosseum, and other third-party services are provided for convenience. Those services have their own privacy policies over which we have no control.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-[11px] tracking-[0.14em] text-[var(--color-ash)] mb-3">COOKIES</h2>
        <p>We set no first-party cookies. Seggwat may set cookies when the feedback widget is loaded.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-[11px] tracking-[0.14em] text-[var(--color-ash)] mb-3">YOUR RIGHTS (GDPR)</h2>
        <p>Under GDPR you have the right to access, rectification, erasure, restriction of processing, data portability, and objection. Contact: <a href="mailto:parnerkarsharang@gmail.com" class="text-[var(--color-phosphor)] hover:underline">parnerkarsharang@gmail.com</a></p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
